description.narrative:
Project outputs: These activities will result in: Under Objective # 1: (1.1.1) Training material developed; (1.1.2) Training for 20 potential mentors conducted; (1.1.3) Potential mentors have practiced the business mentoring skills with real SMEs
Under Objective #2: (2.1.1) Capacity of 20 potential entrepreneurs in business-related fields required to establish and start a small business is developed;
Under Objective #3: (3.1.1) Marketing Plans have been developed for 5 medium-sized enterprises; (3.1.2) Staff at these enterprises have been oriented on using the newly-developed marketing plans (3.2.1) At least 35 small enterprises received coaching on improvement their enterprises performance; (3.2.2) At least 15 small enterprises have developed or revised their business plans
